    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stiff paste often composed of plaster and powdered stone used to fill holes or cover defects in statuary, stone, or wood, usually made from plaster and chalk or from sawdust and strong glue.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
